MEMBERSHIP
Membership Benefits
Free admission to Cedar Lakes Woods & Gardens for one year.
Free or reduced admission to special events, festivals, and workshops.
10% discount on Cedar Lakes Woods & Gardens merchandise items.
Monthly newsletter with updates, event announcements, and exclusive content.
50% off admission at Kanapaha Botanical Garden in Gainesville, FL
Membership Tiers
Individual
: $40.00 – Includes 1 named adult.
Two Adults
: $60.00 – Includes 2 named adults.
Three Adults
: $80.00 – Includes 3 named adults.
Four Adults
: $100.00 – Includes 4 named adults.
Gold Membership
: $200.00 – Includes 2 named adults plus up to 6 guests per day.
Add-Ons
Add 1 child (age 17 and under): $5.00
Add 2 children (age 17 and under): $10.00
Add 3 children (age 17 and under): $15.00
Add 4 children (age 17 and under): $20.00
Important Notes
Once your membership form is submitted, names cannot be changed.
We look forward to welcoming you as a valued member of our gardens!
ONLINE SIGN-UP

Includes one named adult, with a $5 add-on per child applied at checkout.
